        "timestamp": 1761351888
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Actually maybe <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=EuclideanDomain#doc\">docs#EuclideanDomain</a> is almost exactly what I want, except that it doesn't support semirings (nat). It has <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Algebra/EuclideanDomain/Defs.html#EuclideanDomain.instDiv\">EuclideanDomain.instDiv</a></p>",
